article_id:690,category_name:News,title_name:Expedited Construction for New Players Only!,image_path:,message:<div>Starting with the version 1.12.0 update, we added an expedited construction feature for new players where the time required to build and level up facilities in the castle grounds will be halved for 30 days after it is unlocked!</div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);"><strong>Note: This applies to all players who complete the Castle Grounds tutorial and unlock it after the automatic update to version 1.12.0, which was performed at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1569564000"></span>.</strong></span></div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/af1b80c52d4b56c225f89a32278cd1c2.png"></div><div><br></div><div>Note: To unlock the castle grounds, players must clear Ch. 1 / 4-6 (Normal) and complete the tutorial for the Castle Grounds and Dragon&#39;s Roost.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1569564000,update_time1568947135